0:12:46.88,000 --> 0:12:48,000
Brian Eno will reach for one of the cards.

263
0:12:49.2,000 --> 0:12:5,000
He'll draw one at random,

264
0:12:50.68,000 --> 0:12:54,000
and he'll make the band follow the instructions on the card.

265
0:12:54.96,000 --> 0:12:55,000
So this one ...

266
0:12:57.04,000 --> 0:12:58,000
"Change instrument roles."

267
0:12:58.36,000 --> 0:13:,000
Yeah, everyone swap instruments -- Drummer on the piano --

