307
0:15:08.2,000 --> 0:15:09,000
So however we do it ...

308
0:15:10.4,000 --> 0:15:12,000
whether it's sheer willpower,

309
0:15:12.48,000 --> 0:15:14,000
whether it's the flip of a card

