0:15:15.56,000 --> 0:15:18,000
or whether it's a guilt trip from a German teenager,

311
0:15:19.68,000 --> 0:15:21,000
all of us, from time to time,

312
0:15:21.84,000 --> 0:15:25,000
need to sit down and try and play the unplayable piano.

313
0:15:27.64,000 --> 0:15:28,000
